    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed the full 13-factor assessment. All seven assessed factors show achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors remain not-assessed, representing substantial epistemic gaps. The central hemolysis credibility claim (bindsClaim) provides extensive prose referencing Monte Carlo UQ, mesh convergence, and bench validation data, and on prose review appears well-supported. The structured evidence derivation links in the claim node were accepted as implicit given the prose references. On this basis the package is formally accepted pending resolution of the six not-assessed factors in a follow-on assessment cycle.",
